<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢٧-<span class="c5"> أحمد بن أبى فنن:</span> ٤٣٠<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
